                    <td>2:00 PM - 3:30 PM</td>\n                    <td>Session 11: Transformers</td>\n                    <td>Room 103</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td>April 30, 2025 (Wednesday)</td>\n                    <td>4:00 PM - 5:30 PM</td>\n                    <td>Workshop Session 2</td>\n                    <td>Workshop Room 2</td>\n                </tr>\n                 <tr>\n                    <td>May 1, 2025 (Thursday)</td>\n                    <td>9:00 AM - 10:30 AM</td>\n                    <td>Session 12: Meta Learning</td>\n                    <td>Room 104</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td>May 1, 2025 (Thursday)</td>\n                    <td>11:00 AM - 12:30 PM</td>\n                    <td>Session 13: Continual Learning</td>\n                    <td>Room 101</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td>May 1, 2025 (Thursday)</td>\n                    <td>2:00 PM - 3:00 PM</td>\n                    <td>Closing Ceremony & Awards</td>\n                    <td>Grand Ballroom</td>\n                </tr>\n            </tbody>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n</section>\n      ]]>\n    </Content>\n  </Slide>\n  <Slide>\n    <Title>ICLR 2025 - Venue</Title>\n    <Content>\n      <![CDATA[\n<section id=\"venue\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Venue</h2>\n        <p>The International Conference on Learning Representations (ICLR) 2025 will be held at:</p>\n        <address>\n            Moscone Center<br>\n            747 Howard St<br>\n            San Francisco, CA 94103<br>\n            United States\n        </address>\n        \n        <h3>Conference Location</h3>\n        <p>The Moscone Center is located in the heart of downtown San Francisco, within walking distance of major hotels, public transit, and local landmarks. ICLR 2025 attendees will find the location both convenient and accessible.</p>\n\n        <h3>Map</h3>\n        <div class=\"map-container\">\n            <iframe\n                src=\"https://www.google.com/maps?q=Moscone+Center,+747+Howard+St,+San+Francisco,+CA+94103,+USA&output=embed\"\n                width=\"600\"\n                height=\"450\"\n                style=\"border:0;\"\n                allowfullscreen=\"\"\n                loading=\"lazy\">\n            </iframe>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n      ]]>\n    </Content>\n  </Slide>\n  <Slide>\n        <Title>ICLR 2025 - CSS Style</Title>\n        <Content>\n            <![CDATA[\n/* style.css */\nbody {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n    background-color: #f4f4f4;\n    color: #333;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\n.container {\n    width: 80%;\n    margin: auto;\n    overflow: hidden;\n}\n\nheader {\n    background: #333;\n    color: #fff;\n    padding-top: 30px;\n    min-height: 70px;\n    border-bottom: #e8491d 3px solid;\n}\n\nheader a {\n    color: #fff;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    font-size: 16px;\n}\n\nheader ul {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n}\n\nheader li {\n    float: left;\n    display: inline;\n    padding: 0 20px 0 20px;\n}\n\nheader #branding {\n    float: left;\n}\n\nheader #branding h1 {\n    margin: 0;\n}\n\nheader nav {\n    float: right;\n    margin-top: 10px;\n}\n\nheader .highlight, header .current a {\n    color: #e8491d;\n    font-weight: bold;\n}\n\nheader a:hover {\n    color: #ccc;\n    font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n/* Hero Section */\n#hero {\n    background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1600x400') no-repeat center/cover;\n    color: #fff;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding-top: 100px;\n    padding-bottom: 100px;\n}\n\n#hero h1 {\n    font-size: 3em;\n    margin-top: -30px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n/* Organizer Section */\n#organizer {\n    padding: 20px;\n    background: #fff;\n    color: #333;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\n/* Venue Section */\n#venue {\n    padding: 20px;\n    background: #f4f4f4;\n}\n\n#venue .map-container {\n    margin-top: 20px;\n}\n\n/* Schedule Section */\n#schedule {\n    padding: 20px;\n    background: #fff;\n}\n\n#schedule .schedule-table {\n    width: 100%;\n    border-collapse: collapse;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n}\n\n#schedule .schedule-table th, #schedule .schedule-table td {\n    border: 1px solid #ddd;\n    padding: 8px;\n    text-align: left;\n}\n\n#schedule .schedule-table th {\n    background-color: #333;\n    color: white;\n}\n\n/* Footer */\nfooter {\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    color: #fff;\n    background-color: #e8491d;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n            ]]>\n        </Content>\n    </Slide>\n</Presentation>\n```"}
